 Americas saw the strongest regional growth, gaining 4% compared to the 0.8% gain analysts were expecting. Photographer: Victor J. Blue&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2025 年 7 月 18 日星期五，美国纽约 Burberry 旗舰店橱窗里的人体模型。Burberry 在美洲的销售额出现了最强劲的区域增长，增长了 4%，而分析师预期为 0.8%。摄影师：Victor J. Blue&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJHFcGh5YZM8/v7/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt; Burberry 纽约旗舰店。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Victor J. Blue/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;该公司以格子呢围巾和华达呢风衣而闻名，该公司表示，由于对其供应链和行业竞争对手的计划有了更详细的了解，该公司搁置了原定的 2040 年净零排放目标。新的时间表使其与&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/2rk6v5tdcEDA9_ITt8H7js_PNl613kc7lDCFsOlU7so0XQDTFPYbtxP5aFzdL9EgzVKc9gnLiokPqiJvUGkBmmYE2LFKEaqkT_Y_FsiBgDdpwnxbA2qxZjVwsNx8CYeX9EIUeurz1OyY4iDlJ69hmwR67QLp9FL0SMZlMIMPB5GITZzEukDk6Q-eUj--rS-42XQAftZSiMdIexehADrv1m6-QQ34bo7sfW5JKtRh-KfXquCV2-dWwwyaqvZqcfCEqeoKSe27Y3DIqPrB_rEY3ve2Bn65h5k1LLhl-NWdZTz3z460wwHMnokfz3ZIEFkHybLdHT6f5RFjq8WLhFi3DnHJFKVOpmhEfydU3kId8zmKmCrI7YTJMJgzN_ZGF9Vcn0KJlGbfKG0dPNChCnjQBHnEUyM7v3OzFK2rR3qjZ_cYZaRDIL8AZJYI42eYqm29CEcIpl0K8gw2hJHW1Sk/wnf1udn8xgl6jU9PmsFis_iy1vDcL8aW/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="开云集团"&gt;开云集团&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/H9bdM7hOSzQWQNfv_s3MIhhhuo9cJ2TBylWqzDO2-hY8O3C6b270TWVio0wbISOFMngfRLmSuQqR07QhTAqQTuFuC3-JYvTUMBdg1GPsFOPAnvAl97yETeAyR_EAO9XBPoWa4-Hd9UGjbkR3lC2OXIcvVFf16gm3fouLNI3onYsskCh215Rlrf8S0hBJs2_pjiSam8zlQ1CYHGmFW_n43F6iDINsTQEqWyIPxifT7ELAJ-dSD1LJAlQFsaUYocLTM6JgPfm8UNf48JbxDgq8J7Im-yHoGOtd3Vn_-gHF3rTZydGerku15F8iubgN0ZGdIM0VR9fx6YbtUZnP2kbSsYaCaAAp30nCQplYK7_bns4leM0_E9DsWzdO-bUB0BgVqWlRxkQllSVYrktznclK-g_ib_EwDL8_QCATiGJDEJJePHAOdWmoCRJ6CAtcHzyQ_tBSZ8i5sPyzn6s22g/ViE7WILlO5r_2r8OD3yMg7MFqMugMBRN/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="LVMH 酩悦轩尼诗路易威登集团"&gt;路威酩轩集团&lt;/a&gt;等业内同行保持一致。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; Burberry 在周四发布的 2025-2026 年&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xpB3uHgbkqySCHheGwZjoy06QqsfD51zZLkG3mkJXt7PfaLKqYtzQpuo8Q7bhHU0cQS06kaCkr9jkvoEuaatj9l3FZOsIw5HC31OzUTHatBgViK8ZtOUYefIyBBzCrVkiFu3Qak7bla_62r6rRSUXwS6TTRBQsXBL5vhn112x4aHbOBbrDuPgzPxktkJ1WVJmKdqxnzIqAFWcfZqaudnQbu0THLb8yXFn6T3q21XwIAVhtSDg9PwyvR75-i_-XoI8JgUbwYRHKE5wRZlKKIUXmQTpxRCnKV51M85Koz34OWCDWHJ5y21rMU5eLqez4kepblF_sjDTiJNmQTMVKDFqqDR2TcE51K56c5aDC8HCCNvcF_q1vzu4ka9Ke5Ww10woajjRScIzVqq_xvFH-5C-DlgSP8hht-s/Dmv5IlrXq96UWGJQauzIJXjeyfUGLLrh/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;年度报告&lt;/a&gt;中写道：“我们认为，修订后的目标反映了对外部因素的务实反应，同时使我们能够保持与我们对气候变化作为我们业务面临的主要风险的评估相一致的雄心水平。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;近年来，越来越多的各行业公司在气候目标上出现倒退，部分原因是持续的地缘政治动荡对供应链造成破坏。特朗普政府还取消了许多美国气候目标，促使科技巨头和汽车制造商等公司削弱了减少有害排放的努力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Z8TPYFtCJ4T0RiMHWfU5zQjFUynqRmGY4gO3p4zRxI0qHbox4gOv1joQNqWOrIBMu2qxGIXykIJ03evxxq4X23iHHywUTsT7qjyUsznJ0cDaND3vSgwN3mgaKGkBpRTyhkWUqTaiuN3zWzMKUnG_0qjEczM2ME5m35SmZ6PVnYimH6z3J-M-uAcNgHiRYHaDebkrAzHBajoHNRK9Qz9Y8-z_jZt-7NXdzLmt9hLIMyXqYYCkfEx38hJwe1P80GpstfZ9G43NiA35kdLOXkB0H65PONkv7hAWN5ZZJOaA2RXLpcAci3j8IEnbG35J6Puxs5L548XPyaKa6TmeqnB7zQM3-pSDmqFe3LEtSfy1Lp1qRbGj9DtRZT6aoZmeMQDuhRD-8xdq7UiyFnqumyJo/Tg2ysi7bknx37JkJl04Sq8Jf5NUq6sqN/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Burberry 获得 SBTi 批准实现净零排放目标"&gt;五年前，&lt;/a&gt; Burberry 宣布了到 2040 年实现净零排放的目标，领先于其他奢侈品牌和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Uw_TvaxlJMCiiP_MhKVq-S0awQHob3MvZlACK5OgwWFZbUwNEMiNV_BiPoDwWhFEwtK7iSmQjVJZSIq7_QiERzv37dSnaKpr8b472Pk_z6yYgE8YUQrfql2RpV0M-2uKtA7aULWnXGmlLcqUcNVo2Grb6Gj9QtSd-YKnUkVvPy3jxJaSzrVH-Xv-5D1u2ZR784nsOeRLqOhz7BFTbp67YRSDwdolFY-tyVybrQUP1dnKtqH85EX44irPBQ-sBIFwpRar_Vt8519k7xWA6OqWTT5R2vdRD32eUHCaFnB3We___8p9yh41gmmsLLAFNfq1b_AX1Nrpo5k/FlaERQ5MMSEt9zwOfDK5eQHGR4_NXBks/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;《巴黎气候变化协议》&lt;/a&gt; ，从而将自己定位为行业领导者。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随后，香奈儿 (Chanel) 和时尚零售商&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/g5ZcKhKMmF3MDp-0SSxPbqhHr0bqdrPvQxdGIYt9LGbvk_f8-BQNQAMO3X6oR3i2rVJNdm6EVuk_Lt7qUb42JCG7MR3qbyktfqrHPcPzx6rezCfdwMc5gbQpNDZb9NzvEi0hGrdfFzoPPHHPRBa729G1bDMwmpURI75V5XUpbGc8rz_E6BKinLvsO4ejyMHZZroAHYnJ3uFHtXluXtAWLR5SB3S4BoKZo9BIV4Z4dpEQ3DdG-jt6Xd5Mcbc2sm_-Sd8ksbHRBEdWYYPnnXXAeiOJ6LrI3Q_uU16hh8FbTvbGSAojM-o5MVMTLRCa952zaQ0SD-00uqOUfK93QVutrQoAsvKGUjfn1ezFN8yyoLzzgxizvN3IL-s8_OAFeE1aBdwSWN6Neyrpr5EYwcESr-lp2-h2CgMMMS7Pa8dAa5WikP1xhbEHntClGxjTmBw6i_L-KFjcd1mENxcvoA8/qVI9fCNQUp5YNkAFsAVYGHO-siviqXQb/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="亚索斯公司"&gt;ASOS Plc&lt;/a&gt;也加入了英国品牌的行列，宣布了 2040 年的目标，而旗下拥有古驰 (Gucci) 和巴黎世家 (Balenciaga) 等品牌的开云集团 (Kering) 和路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 则维持了 2050 年的目标。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; Burberry 周四发布的另一份&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ys9RqMGO5VOQBlRFUGMvusV3X_HSybVNaQH65DkcXXlV1bpc51v7xeEqzi0EhrjCQlm2zvDUV6-hFCotEYKCt2CDCDf5C9U856YuwLs7Y4UAsQkVuJF4O54vXqkKLBcIpxoiBvg2Z0loDb1FTZwF1qRL-3NQsWmF54z4VPzvp6XpKOJf_YyYQrLNfYMeU6WJcVD3KO_0oR2nrWSK6PmHmHncFZCGoinqXRarA5T4xLwb57dH43kyiYtQKLOdtZl5o7ZZs3i9R0v8YWb15GdmdWJywdRYsLbOralh2fYObtCNk3ZqS0dhSWQBXGWU4P0lkLreY1JvX4im6FGeSjjUEdgCtz8DjJQ6YMXUu_UACsFoVZZgvX5Vov__pLihF8SABJz4CZTPl3hGKopIDg/AGGgfuEKqCuWArMZVKLRl2A-ML9MxRQH/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;报告&lt;/a&gt;详细介绍了该公司如何在明年之前将其自身业务的排放量减少 95%。根据新的气候转型计划，价值链的其余减排量——90%在能源和工业领域，72%在森林、土地和农业领域——将在2050年底前实现。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;该公司将向&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/bxpl4i3nC8wWMaSMSQtKuFqKyPC4IqvLf2oeG0wETCbsOCJBqoHBsbHbhIgRLE9jHY1cOG4oNoTlPaPn-MxMN2N9yrsOObe6vtZ3Qf7OP-0k4xAVhxmB6xd6nOpL2wZqkgEV1xV-CLo0ehzFQudMuW_yJaaeryYMw6QZ0W6NWW4oYmtzRyjVkJBZV_9ZJ57L5FRLHa-t380wk0UiZkgncBInD0k8Nx1nYIfL31N2kBPbcSxkW4vepbW4aguHQOOWZ1jPQVrXBIUytGijCWGuM-UP5y79q0eVUprjfR4qtlcdKYnVmg/eYCKgAkY34iqvuc5HjjRAyXn6B2ptqQi/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="关于我们"&gt;科学目标倡议组织&lt;/a&gt;(SBTi) 提交修订后的目标，该组织致力于帮助企业实现《巴黎协定》中规定的温室气体减排目标。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 20px;" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" style="padding: 0;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5xNw-JemaE55-2lHh61wnLV86cE51ZZaMezEZr6-tJZ2oVPcgReomrch8d7CAwKSW4LO84JBslhGfP9p92UB7jNgwwsEVRMOg3b7zStwusg2abEXkFrSlQGW_czVyFIRSriaz1I6NoVXMfI_njJ1BLMY2OWIUOx7zp5Cqz0EWKi9xT-7YLCpiwQR0uWViW8YRs6rG2EJ7AmdiKbTqpLOBT0UJ2vuBzlqoxm9xJe2i7q3UsqES-erIauUfjXM90ZYLDsGv2suN5O2OlSnvHxyKRxMSI2ir0tfWRBhgKs5I8bMohv5M5xCeH6G3McAmsT7VJCTSHGWdo7KWt4lkxp_54Gx53SIPb61mCClhfWR_DQyMIGQC-JjnC15dI_d0WH8LcWzbYbO-U4_T84ak5mrVGXy5uVxkw9N_Fj15CqVz4N40r2c7HeLmBjhjptMFYaR1E3hnHi_Nvna8m8V/yQatvbfXBnUcbE0IP6EbouITCybcDiCT/21" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" border="0" class="mq-lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=868582&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=desktop&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=18337824&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=05292026143821&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6" style="display: block; height: auto; width: 100%;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&